<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Not really, the first book takes place with Pearl and May, (aunt/mother) and Joy up to college age. The second book is about Joy but does touch on eve<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Not really, the first book takes place with Pearl and May, (aunt/mother) and Joy up to college age. The second book is about Joy but does touch on events from first book. I think not reading first book would be missing out.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
